{"tid":2147233,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"[傳真社消息]林鄭幼子林約希上月25日後行蹤不明 曾在Facebook向室友稱「家有急事」回港","createTime":"2020-08-09T06:11:02.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-09T16:08:18.000Z","uid":105567,"like":5,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"48c42524cc93451879cb5caaf57c3d28218637ba","tid":2147233,"uid":105567,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-09T06:11:02.000Z","msg":"【特首兒子消息】美國財政部香港時間周五(7日)晚上向行政長官林鄭月娥等11名中港官員實施制裁，外界關注林鄭月娥身處美國修讀博士的幼子林約希去向。傳真社派員到當地嘗試與林約希接觸，得悉他約於上月25日失蹤，室友其後透過Facebook收到他聲稱「家有急事」回港。他27日曾電郵回覆業主會續租單位至2021年8月，但之後一直失聯，現時行蹤不明。特首辦至截稿前未有回覆。<br />\n傳真社記者到訪林約希位於美國波士頓的住址，並聯絡到其業主。業主稱，林的室友約在7月25日表示與林失去聯絡數天，向她查詢會否知道林的去向。業主其後致電林，卻被接駁到當地電訊商Verizon第24號公告，內容指「由於線路限制，此通話未能成功撥出」(This call cannot be completed because there are restrictions on this line. Announcement 24)，未能成功聯絡上。<br />\n業主指，室友7月27日告知已透過Facebook找到林，並轉達他因「家有急事」(family emergency)返回香港。<br />\n足本報道：<a href=\"https://bit.ly/3aaO7RB\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F3aaO7RB&d=SXj%2FfRDdIS6Y9psqMYminNmOP5%2FvN4RyP%2Fy1e26q30o%3D&h=5b677ba6\" target=\"_blank\">https://bit.ly/3aaO7RB</a>"},{"pid":"5695fcfa73e571b5acd6a09f3c937352ab52fc6f","tid":2147233,"uid":105567,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-09T06:11:14.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/factwire/videos/363915694608474\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Ffactwire%2Fvideos%2F363915694608474&d=SXj%2FfRDdIS6Y9psqMYminNmOP5%2FvN4RyP%2Fy1e26q30o%3D&h=1745b32c\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/factwire/videos/363915694608474</a>"},{"pid":"76d70ab34116b661a3e211fa38b4e9ccd090657e","tid":2147233,"uid":259532,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-09T06:31:43.000Z","msg":"你還有黨啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/free.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0ef1ba7bf5921eb68ad313d5f79c2fc8d9264d90","tid":2147233,"uid":73092,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-09T06:34:0